My friends, The Lord Jesus Christ is coming! Hallelujah! 
Repent of your sins and put your faith in Jesus! 

Jesus Loves you, friends. He is not angry at you, and neither does He hate you. Those are lies from the devil. Please don't let anyone or anything stop you from coming to Jesus. 

He has delivered us from our sins, by dying for us on the cross. He punished sin, by His Own Body. Thank You, Jesus!

He rose again the 3rd day, assuring us of our redemption. He got the Victory over death! Death can no longer hold Him down, and neither will it hold you down if you accept Jesus as your Lord and Savior! Hallelujah! 

Friends, The Lord is coming, but we might go to Him today. So if you don't know Jesus as your Lord and Savior, please make today you change that. He will forgive you of ALL sins in your life. You just have to trust Him. 

He will also deliver you from the oncoming Judgement that is quickly approaching this earth. He made a Way to escape, by His Body on the cross. Thank You, Jesus. 

To die without Jesus is very dangerous. So make the wisest decision of your life  today by calling upon Jesus! You will be saved! Just call upon Him from the heart! 

Shalom!
